---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import ListHeader from "../components/ListHeader.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with Ewen Quimerch">
  <ListHeader />
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">Contact</h2>

      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg">
        <p class="text-white/90 mb-8 text-center text-lg">
          Feel free to reach out through any of these channels:
        </p>

        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/EwenQuim"
            class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors group text-text-link dark:text-text-link-dark hover:text-text-link-hover dark:hover:text-text-link-hover-dark no-underline"
          >
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-current"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold font-sans transition-colors">GitHub</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Check out my projects</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a
            href="#"
            data-contact="ZXdlbi5xdWltZXJjaCtoZWxsb0BAZ21haWxAY29t"
            data-subj="W0FOVEktU1BBTSBUQUddIEhlbGxvICE="
            onfocus="this.href = 'mailto:' + atob(this.dataset.contact).replaceAll('@', '.').replaceAll('@.', '@') + '?subject=' + atob(this.dataset.subj || '')"
            class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors group text-text-link dark:text-text-link-dark hover:text-text-link-hover dark:hover:text-text-link-hover-dark no-underline"
          >
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-current"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold font-sans transition-colors">Email</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
                Send me a direct message
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ewen-quimerch/"
            class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors group text-text-link dark:text-text-link-dark hover:text-text-link-hover dark:hover:text-text-link-hover-dark no-underline"
          >
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-current"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold font-sans transition-colors">
                LinkedIn
              </h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
                Connect with me professionally
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/rss.xml"
            class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors group text-text-link dark:text-text-link-dark hover:text-text-link-hover dark:hover:text-text-link-hover-dark no-underline"
          >
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-current"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  d="M6.503 20.752c0 1.794-1.456 3.248-3.251 3.248-1.796 0-3.252-1.454-3.252-3.248 0-1.794 1.456-3.248 3.252-3.248 1.795.001 3.251 1.454 3.251 3.248zm-6.503-12.572v4.811c6.05.062 10.96 4.966 11.022 11.009h4.817c-.062-8.71-7.118-15.758-15.839-15.82zm0-3.368c10.58.046 19.152 8.594 19.183 19.188h4.817c-.03-13.231-10.755-23.954-24-24v4.812z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold font-sans transition-colors">
                RSS Feed
              </h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
                Subscribe to my latest posts
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">
            I'm always interested in discussing new opportunities,
            collaborations, or just having a chat about technology and software
            engineering.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- About Section -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 text-center">
        About Me
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-8 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-white/90">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
            Software Engineer & Problem Solver
          </h3>

          <p class="mb-6">
            I'm a passionate software engineer with a strong foundation in
            computer science from École Centrale, one of France's most
            prestigious engineering schools. I specialize in building scalable,
            high-performance systems using modern technologies like Go, Rust,
            TypeScript, and React.
          </p>

          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">
            Professional Experience
          </h4>

          <p class="mb-4">
            My career has been focused on solving complex technical challenges
            for enterprise clients. At CMA-CGM, I developed comprehensive
            digital solutions for global container shipping operations, building
            on microservices that handle millions of tracking requests daily.
            The system I architected dramatically improved booking behavior:
            last-minute cancellations (within 3 days of departure) dropped from
            57% to under 5%, while early cancellations (more than a week in
            advance) increased to 82% after just 5 weeks of implementation. This
            transformation significantly enhanced operational efficiency and
            resource planning.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-6">
            Currently, I'm working on a new banking solution for professionals,
            the brand new digital bank of LCL (Le Crédit Lyonnais), focusing on
            modern financial services platforms that prioritize security,
            compliance, exceptional user experience and data intelligence. These
            projects have given me deep expertise in building mission-critical
            systems that operate at scale.
          </p>

          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">
            Technical Expertise
          </h4>

          <p class="mb-4">
            I'm particularly passionate about systems programming with Go and
            Rust, where I can leverage their performance characteristics and
            safety features to build robust backend services. On the frontend, I
            work with React and TypeScript to create intuitive user interfaces
            that make complex systems accessible to end users.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-6">
            My experience spans the full technology stack: from designing
            microservices architectures and implementing CI/CD pipelines, to
            optimizing database performance and ensuring system reliability
            through comprehensive monitoring and observability practices.
          </p>

          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Beyond Code</h4>

          <p class="mb-4">
            When I'm not coding, I enjoy writing technical articles and short
            stories, exploring the intersection of technology and creativity. I
            believe that clear communication and storytelling are essential
            skills for any engineer, whether you're documenting complex systems
            or presenting solutions to stakeholders.
          </p>

          <p>
            I'm always interested in discussing new technologies, architectural
            patterns, and the evolving landscape of software engineering. Feel
            free to reach out if you'd like to connect or collaborate on
            interesting projects.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
